      <title>美国数据显示，由于流动性稀薄，新兴市场资产小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/emerging-assets-edge-lower-amid-thin-liquidity-us-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场资产周一小幅走低，原因是美国最新数据和全球流动性依然稀薄，欧洲、澳大利亚和香港的多个市场周一因复活节休市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/emerging-assets-edge-lower-amid-thin-liquidity-us-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 14:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
