    <item>
      <title>巴尔的摩船舶事故导致东海岸港口争相吸收货物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/baltimore-ship-accident-has-east-coast-ports-scrambling-to-absorb-cargo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国东海岸港口正在调整其运营方式，以吸收从巴尔的摩港转移的货物，那里的打捞专家已开始清除被毁坏的弗朗西斯·斯科特基桥上的碎片，当局正在建立一条临时通道以重新开放交通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/baltimore-ship-accident-has-east-coast-ports-scrambling-to-absorb-cargo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 16:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
